{"id": 1561, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今，你觉得真正“有文化”的表现是什么？", "description": "至少应该要这样，才能勉强算个“文化人”吧。（题图来自：Vivien Mildenberger ​​​​）", "record_count": 7329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170310130040KeECHlJXuOm9bNS7.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-03-20T03:00:41Z", "options": [{"id": 213504, "content": "心里住着一个小孩和一个老人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1047489}, {"id": 181504, "content": "有真正文化者必见义勇为，必热爱读书，必谈吐儒雅，必敢于向社会发声。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 976676}, {"id": 181505, "content": "知道刷牙的时候不莽（漱口水不要溅到人）。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725763}, {"id": 181761, "content": "看穿不说穿。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896910}, {"id": 182017, "content": "言行平凡大众，思维广阔灵活，文化不是面子，而是里子", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977760}, {"id": 181506, "content": "最好的修养，是明知不问。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 968176}, {"id": 181507, "content": "知识面广，有独特的逻辑链条。", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210313}, {"id": 181763, "content": "会忍耐\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977044}, {"id": 182019, "content": "心胸豁达，明事知礼，智慧又善良的人。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977762}, {"id": 181508, "content": "写字漂亮", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 892970}, {"id": 181764, "content": "不骄不躁，不吹不黑", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 975153}, {"id": 182532, "content": "关键是素质，教养，没有人会拉着人让他做卷子来看他有没文化。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979312}, {"id": 186372, "content": "微笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 989624}, {"id": 181765, "content": "去厕所后会冲厕", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698262}, {"id": 183301, "content": "真正做到雅俗共赏", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981058}, {"id": 183557, "content": "不以物喜，不以己悲。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981764}, {"id": 184325, "content": "谈吐教养素质心态和精神面貌，以貌取人并不全是贬义", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 983683}, {"id": 181766, "content": "不急不躁\n有文化自然有礼貌", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 94455}, {"id": 182022, "content": "好好说话不装逼不说脏话的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977773}, {"id": 182278, "content": "学习并传播优秀的传统文化，了解学习其他民族的文化并将其有益部分整合到自己的文化里。是能够适应时代的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 971406}, {"id": 181511, "content": "遇到难题的时候不是抱怨命运，也不埋怨别人，而是低头做事", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 976687}, {"id": 198152, "content": "适度的隐忍成习惯。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1011736}, {"id": 208904, "content": "返璞归真，不再在意华丽的形式", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 809902}, {"id": 181512, "content": "素质", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 793857}, {"id": 181768, "content": "学习众多别人的想法  仍然有自己的思维", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977078}, {"id": 183560, "content": "遇事淡定不毛躁", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981781}, {"id": 187144, "content": "坚持阅读", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 985401}, {"id": 181513, "content": "谈吐素养不一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 976691}, {"id": 181769, "content": "能从周边的空气中区别各种没文化的银！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 777364}, {"id": 182025, "content": "无论是哪方面的东西，都能与别人进行交谈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 964590}, {"id": 181514, "content": "有容乃大", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 407163}, {"id": 181770, "content": "见人说人话，见鬼说鬼话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977084}, {"id": 181515, "content": "腹有诗书气自华 美而不自知", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 976692}, {"id": 181771, "content": "见人说人话，见鬼说鬼话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977084}, {"id": 181516, "content": "有内涵的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972956}, {"id": 181772, "content": "理性思考，有主见", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 861663}, {"id": 182028, "content": "  文化，不同人文化不同，理解也不同，对文化这词的含义表达也不同。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977643}, {"id": 181517, "content": "遇到一件事时，头脑清晰，不乱，稳得住！再一个，平日的时间里总是能够温文尔雅，不快不慢，张弛有度！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 608744}, {"id": 181518, "content": "懂得好，热爱美", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972173}, {"id": 181774, "content": "做事有底线", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915864}, {"id": 181519, "content": "险不惊于心，喜不形于色", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 942283}, {"id": 181775, "content": "处变不惊，一切从容面对", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977106}, {"id": 181264, "content": "不对常识感到惊讶", "image": null, "praise_count": 275, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855068}, {"id": 181520, "content": "有思想，而不只是有神经中枢", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 976700}, {"id": 181776, "content": "会系统阅读", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977108}, {"id": 182800, "content": "足够客观", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 894397}, {"id": 187152, "content": "宠辱不惊 出门带脑子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991833}, {"id": 181265, "content": "谈吐质量明显与他人不同，不为卖弄。真生气也不会骂脏话", "image": null, "praise_count": 939, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770610}, {"id": 181777, "content": "有个人魅力，言谈举止，谈笑风生。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977107}, {"id": 182033, "content": "不依赖，不卖弄\n宽容大气又坚守原则", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977808}]}